---
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container about-inner">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p class="section-label">Über uns</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">
        Kein gewöhnliches Café.<br />
        <em>Napoli in Erlangen.</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="about-body">
        Stefania's Cafè è nata da un sogno: portare la tradizione di Napoli fin qui,
        a Erlangen. Dal caffè al dolce, passando per vini e aperitivi.
        Un posto semplice, curato in ogni dettaglio, dove si mangia davvero bene.
      </p>
      <p class="about-body de">
        Stefanias Cafè entstand aus dem Traum, die Kultur meiner Stadt Neapel
        nach Deutschland zu bringen. Vom Kaffee bis zu den typischen Süßspeisen,
        sowie Wein und Aperitive. Jedes Detail ist gepflegt — genau wie unser Menü.
        Frische Zutaten, alles selbst gemacht.
      </p>
      <div class="about-badges">
        <div class="badge">
          <span class="badge-num">100%</span>
          <span class="badge-label">Hausgemacht</span>
        </div>
        <div class="badge">
          <span class="badge-num">Napoli</span>
          <span class="badge-label">Tradition seit 1983</span>
        </div>
        <div class="badge">
          <span class="badge-num">Erlangen</span>
          <span class="badge-label">Schiffstraße 12</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-image">
      <img src="/img/menu-colazione.jpg" alt="Frühstückstafel bei Stefania's Cafè" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: var(--section-pad);
    background: var(--color-light);
  }

  .about-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-body {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .about-body.de {
    color: #7a6260;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-badges {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .badge {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .badge-num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .badge-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #9a7a75;
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
  }

  .about-image {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
  }

  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
  }

  .about-image::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: -1.5rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    z-index: -1;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .about-image {
      aspect-ratio: 4/3;
      order: -1;
    }

    .about-image::before {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
